overview.en: FEB (Fair Efficient Business) will subvert the traditional big data industry model and establish an advanced, safe and unique decentralized data industry ecology. Through open rules and clear standards, FEB aims to accelerate the flow of industrial information, optimize the current industrial structure, rationally allocate resources, and finally realize to form a decentralized platform based on the FEB protocol.
overview.zh: FEB（Fair Efficient Business），中文名，飞币。其将颠覆传统大数据产业模式，建立一个先进、安全、独特的去中心化数大据产业生态，FEB希望通过一系列公开公正的规则标准，促进整个产业信息快速流动变更，优化当前产业结构组成、对资源进行合理分配，最终实现利用区块链技术形成以FEB协议为节点的去中心化平台，最终打造成为一个服务全球的顶级大数据产业平台。
